---
title: Seared Salmon & Leek-Caper Sauce with Chive Mash
description: Don't let this dish be the one that got away! With a fragrant leek and caper sauce over succulent salmon, plus chive mash,  pan-fried veggies and a dill and lemon crumb to finish, it's a great catch.

*Unfortunately, this week's green beans were in short supply, so we've replaced them with baby spinach leaves. Don't worry, the recipe will be just as delicious!*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/seared-salmon-leek-caper-sauce-8a1a85cc.jpg
